room_title: Escape room "Heirless Throne" by Behind Locked Doors in Quincy
room_description: The King of Broad passed away in the night and left behind no heir. No sons or daughters did he have, and no wife either. His sisters and brothers have gathered to determine who is the rightful king or queen, but the kingdom is in chaos, as all of Broad is fighting for the right to the throne and attempting to prove that they are the true heir to the throne. Will you find the true heir in time or will the Kingdom of Broad be doomed for eternity?
